      <title>在佛罗里达州，人们逃离不断高涨的反移民情绪</title>
      <link>https://npr.org/2024/04/24/1236631178/in-florida-an-exodus-of-people-fleeing-rising-anti-immigrant-sentiment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大约一年前，佛罗里达州通过了该国最严格的移民法之一。在一些社区，这导致了大规模人口外流。那些留下来的人说，这让生活变得可怕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://npr.org/2024/04/24/1236631178/in-florida-an-exodus-of-people-fleeing-rising-anti-immigrant-sentiment</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 20:45:42 GMT</pubDate>
